{"tid":2320414,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"歐盟斷然拒絕中國橫蠻無理的要求 禁止批評中共的學者出席歐中貿易論壇 現決定乾脆取消它","createTime":"2020-12-10T20:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T04:34:50.000Z","uid":28114,"like":50,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3660713717e896def2e7e7d8b9815d852d03850d","tid":2320414,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:29:30.000Z","msg":"China-Europe Trade Forum Canceled After China Sought to Bar Critics<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-europe-trade-forum-canceled-after-china-sought-to-bar-critics-11607601609?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fchina-europe-trade-forum-canceled-after-china-sought-to-bar-critics-11607601609%3F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=78ddb445\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-europe-trade-forum-canceled-after-china-sought-to-bar-critics-11607601609?</a><br />\n------------------------<br />\nAn annual China-Europe trade forum was quietly canceled last month after European organizers rejected Chinese demands to ban participants critical of Beijing.<br />\nThe move, not previously reported, highlights an increasingly difficult balance Europe is trying to strike between safeguarding business interests and upholding democratic values in the face of China&rsquo;s increasingly aggressive global stance. The U.S. and Australia have taken more forceful stands against pressure from China, sparking public fights and trade battles.<br />\n..........<br />\nOfficials familiar with the exchange say the two people Beijing wanted to exclude from this year&rsquo;s virtual event were Reinhard B&uuml;tikofer, the European Parliament&rsquo;s chairman of the EU-China caucus who has publicly criticized Beijing over Hong Kong and its treatment of the Uighur minority; and Mikko Huotari, the head of Merics, a German think tank critical of the Chinese Communist Party.<br />\n<br />\n戰狼又贏！"},{"pid":"235e34c6856255da8c96acef1325b7cb4b0e4e59","tid":2320414,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:30:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6a930b47518eb66a50eaa650a7da619e7864e1d","tid":2320414,"uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:30:41.000Z","msg":"上個月既事wo"},{"pid":"08a084d3eece715e352937ca568287aa2d10d7ef","tid":2320414,"uid":128151,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"3660713717e896def2e7e7d8b9815d852d03850d","tid":2320414,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:29:30.000Z","msg":"China-Europe Trade Forum Canceled After China Sought to Bar Critics<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-europe-trade-forum-canceled-after-china-sought-to-bar-critics-11607601609?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fchina-europe-trade-forum-canceled-after-china-sought-to-bar-critics-11607601609%3F&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqfGl%2B26pDsgLotMYn9d4AWI%3D&h=78ddb445\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/china-europe-trade-forum-canceled-after-china-sought-to-bar-critics-11607601609?</a><br />\n------------------------<br />\nAn annual China-Europe trade forum was quietly canceled last month after European organizers rejected Chinese demands to ban participants critical of Beijing.<br />\nThe move, not previously reported, highlights an increasingly difficult balance Europe is trying to strike between safeguarding business interests and upholding democratic values in the face of China&rsquo;s increasingly aggressive global stance. The U.S. and Australia have taken more forceful stands against pressure from China, sparking public fights and trade battles.<br />\n..........<br />\nOfficials familiar with the exchange say the two people Beijing wanted to exclude from this year&rsquo;s virtual event were Reinhard B&uuml;tikofer, the European Parliament&rsquo;s chairman of the EU-China caucus who has publicly criticized Beijing over Hong Kong and its treatment of the Uighur minority; and Mikko Huotari, the head of Merics, a German think tank critical of the Chinese Communist Party.<br />\n<br />\n戰狼又贏！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:31:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E5gRF6N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE5gRF6N.gif&h=6da00d32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vMusMQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vMusMQ.gif&h=9a325237&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uNKoxdw.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuNKoxdw.gif&h=d59289ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6a77345f4bef227a296444942aca93f2ac691765","tid":2320414,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c6a930b47518eb66a50eaa650a7da619e7864e1d","tid":2320414,"uid":14503,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:30:41.000Z","msg":"上個月既事wo"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:32:11.000Z","msg":"但冇報道過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能EU想低調處理"},{"pid":"21471d66e94dc4d2b9fd7884b4b62c2f74e8fb6e","tid":2320414,"uid":124983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:33:16.000Z","msg":"好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc81bf3d3750b2d6ecc5c25dae3d73bf7f547f5","tid":2320414,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:37:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc3cad14b1357a390ae6c8f840b41c9fce9d5e7b","tid":2320414,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20:42:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ded817bd95354a652960192a4713d91d33238ae4","tid":2320414,"uid":282569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T20